                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d161">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">White</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-03-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 28, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>United States will agree to prohibit their citizens hunting seal within 10 miles
                    of Russian coasts and within zone of 30 miles around Commander and Robbin
                    islands, annual catch on islands to be limited to 30,000; that Russian officers
                    may seize offending American vessels, turning them over to United States for
                    trial. Agreement to be terminated at will by either party on notice.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
